'''FISBA AG''' is a Swiss [[photonics]] company designing and manufacturing optical components and systems.

As of 2015, FISBA was reported to be the world market leader in certain niche markets such as fast axis [[Collimated light|collimators]]. It employed 350 people in [[St. Gallen]].<ref name="NZZ 18 July 2015">{{cite news|last1=Schmutz|first1=Christoph G.|title=Ostschweizer Optik-Cluster: Eine St. Galler Firma bringt Licht in die Glasfaser|url=http://www.nzz.ch/wirtschaft/unternehmen/eine-st-galler-firma-bringt-licht-in-die-glasfaser-1.18581783|accessdate=19 July 2015|work=[[Neue Zürcher Zeitung]]|date=18 July 2015|language=German}}</ref>

